7975 static void UI_StopCinematic(int handle)
7976 {
7977  if (handle >= 0)
7978  {
7979  trap_CIN_StopCinematic(handle);
7980  }
7981  else
7982  {
7983  handle = abs(handle);
7984  if (handle == UI_MAPCINEMATIC)
7985  {
7986  if (uiInfo.mapList[ui_currentMap.integer].cinematic >= 0)
7987  {
7988  trap_CIN_StopCinematic(uiInfo.mapList[ui_currentMap.integer].cinematic);
7989  uiInfo.mapList[ui_currentMap.integer].cinematic = -1;
7990  }
7991  }
7992  else if (handle == UI_NETMAPCINEMATIC)
7993  {
7994  if (uiInfo.serverStatus.currentServerCinematic >= 0)
7995  {
7996  trap_CIN_StopCinematic(uiInfo.serverStatus.currentServerCinematic);
7997  uiInfo.serverStatus.currentServerCinematic = -1;
7998  }
7999  }
8000  else if (handle == UI_CLANCINEMATIC)
8001  {
8002  int i = UI_TeamIndexFromName(UI_Cvar_VariableString("ui_teamName"));
8003 
8004  if (i >= 0 && i < uiInfo.teamCount)
8005  {
8006  if (uiInfo.teamList[i].cinematic >= 0)
8007  {
8008  trap_CIN_StopCinematic(uiInfo.teamList[i].cinematic);
8009  uiInfo.teamList[i].cinematic = -1;
8010  }
8011  }
8012  }
8013  }
8014 }

8044 void UI_Init(int legacyClient, int clientVersion)
8045 {
8046  int x;
8047  Com_Printf(S_COLOR_MDGREY "Initializing Legacy ui " S_COLOR_GREEN ETLEGACY_VERSION "\n");
8048 
8049  UI_RegisterCvars();
8050  UI_InitMemory();
8051  trap_PC_RemoveAllGlobalDefines();
8052 
8053  trap_Cvar_Set("ui_menuFiles", "ui/menus.txt"); // we need to hardwire for wolfMP
8054 
8055  // cache redundant calulations
8056  trap_GetGlconfig(&uiInfo.uiDC.glconfig);
8057 
8058  UI_ParseGLConfig();
8059 
8060  // for 640x480 virtualized screen
8061  uiInfo.uiDC.yscale = uiInfo.uiDC.glconfig.vidHeight * (1.0f / 480.0f);
8062  uiInfo.uiDC.xscale = uiInfo.uiDC.glconfig.vidWidth * (1.0f / 640.0f);
8063  if (uiInfo.uiDC.glconfig.vidWidth * SCREEN_HEIGHT > uiInfo.uiDC.glconfig.vidHeight * SCREEN_WIDTH)
8064  {
8065  // wide screen
8066  uiInfo.uiDC.bias = 0.5f * (uiInfo.uiDC.glconfig.vidWidth - (uiInfo.uiDC.glconfig.vidHeight * (640.0f / 480.0f)));
8067  }
8068  else
8069  {
8070  // no wide screen
8071  uiInfo.uiDC.bias = 0;
8072  }
8073 
8074  MOD_CHECK_LEGACY(legacyClient, clientVersion, uiInfo.legacyClient);
8075 
8076  if (uiInfo.legacyClient <= 0)
8077  {
8078  uiInfo.uiDC.glconfig.windowAspect = (float)uiInfo.uiDC.glconfig.vidWidth / (float)uiInfo.uiDC.glconfig.vidHeight;
8079  }
8080 
8081  //UI_Load();
8082  uiInfo.uiDC.registerShaderNoMip = &trap_R_RegisterShaderNoMip;
8083  uiInfo.uiDC.setColor = &trap_R_SetColor;
8084  uiInfo.uiDC.drawHandlePic = &UI_DrawHandlePic;
8085  uiInfo.uiDC.drawStretchPic = &trap_R_DrawStretchPic;
8086  uiInfo.uiDC.drawText = &Text_Paint;
8087  uiInfo.uiDC.drawTextExt = &Text_Paint_Ext;
8088  uiInfo.uiDC.textWidth = &Text_Width;
8089  uiInfo.uiDC.textWidthExt = &Text_Width_Ext;
8090  uiInfo.uiDC.multiLineTextWidth = &Multiline_Text_Width;
8091  uiInfo.uiDC.textHeight = &Text_Height;
8092  uiInfo.uiDC.textHeightExt = &Text_Height_Ext;
8093  uiInfo.uiDC.multiLineTextHeight = &Multiline_Text_Height;
8094  uiInfo.uiDC.textFont = &Text_SetActiveFont;
8095  uiInfo.uiDC.registerModel = &trap_R_RegisterModel;
8096  uiInfo.uiDC.modelBounds = &trap_R_ModelBounds;
8097  uiInfo.uiDC.fillRect = &UI_FillRect;
8098  uiInfo.uiDC.drawRect = &_UI_DrawRect;
8099  uiInfo.uiDC.drawSides = &_UI_DrawSides;

8228 void UI_KeyEvent(int key, qboolean down)
8229 {
8230  static qboolean bypassKeyClear = qfalse;
8231 
8232  if (Menu_Count() > 0)
8233  {
8234  menuDef_t *menu = Menu_GetFocused();
8235  if (menu)
8236  {
8237  if (trap_Cvar_VariableValue("cl_bypassMouseInput") != 0.f)
8238  {
8239  bypassKeyClear = qtrue;
8240  }
8241 
8242  // always have the menus do the proper handling
8243  Menu_HandleKey(menu, key, down);
8244  }
8245  else
8246  {
8247  trap_Key_SetCatcher(trap_Key_GetCatcher() & ~KEYCATCH_UI);
8248 
8249  // we don't want to clear key states if bypassing input
8250  if (!bypassKeyClear)
8251  {
8252  trap_Key_ClearStates();
8253  }
8254 
8255  if (cl_bypassMouseInput.integer)
8256  {
8257  if (!trap_Key_GetCatcher())
8258  {
8259  trap_Cvar_Set("cl_bypassMouseInput", 0);
8260  }
8261  }
8262 
8263  bypassKeyClear = qfalse;
8264 
8265  trap_Cvar_Set("cl_paused", "0");
8266  }
8267  }
8268 }
8269 
8275 void UI_MouseEvent(int dx, int dy)
8276 {
8277  // update mouse screen position
8278  uiInfo.uiDC.cursorx += dx;
8279  if (uiInfo.uiDC.cursorx < 0)
8280  {
8281  uiInfo.uiDC.cursorx = 0;
8282  }
8283  else if (uiInfo.uiDC.cursorx > Cui_WideX(SCREEN_WIDTH))
8284  {
8285  uiInfo.uiDC.cursorx = (int)(Cui_WideX(SCREEN_WIDTH));
8286  }
8287 
8288  uiInfo.uiDC.cursory += dy;
8289  if (uiInfo.uiDC.cursory < 0)
8290  {
8291  uiInfo.uiDC.cursory = 0;
8292  }
8293  else if (uiInfo.uiDC.cursory > SCREEN_HEIGHT)
8294  {
8295  uiInfo.uiDC.cursory = SCREEN_HEIGHT;
8296  }
8297 
8298  if (Menu_Count() > 0)
8299  {
8300  Display_MouseMove(NULL, uiInfo.uiDC.cursorx, uiInfo.uiDC.cursory);
8301  }
8302 }

8315 #define MISSING_FILES_MSG "The following packs are missing:"
8316 
8321 void UI_SetActiveMenu(uiMenuCommand_t menu)
8322 {
8323  char buf[4096]; // com_errorMessage can go up to 4096
8324  char *missing_files;
8325 
8326  // this should be the ONLY way the menu system is brought up
8327  // enusure minumum menu data is cached
8328  if (Menu_Count() > 0)
8329  {
8330  menutype = menu;
8331 
8332  switch (menu)
8333  {
8334  case UIMENU_NONE:
8335  trap_Key_SetCatcher(trap_Key_GetCatcher() & ~KEYCATCH_UI);
8336  trap_Key_ClearStates();
8337  trap_Cvar_Set("cl_paused", "0");
8338  Menus_CloseAll();
8339 
8340  return;
8341  case UIMENU_MAIN:
8342  trap_Key_SetCatcher(KEYCATCH_UI);
8343  Menus_CloseAll();
8344  Menus_ActivateByName("backgroundmusic", qtrue); // not nice, but best way to do it - putting the music in it's own menudef
8345  Menus_ActivateByName("main_opener", qtrue);
8346 
8347  trap_Cvar_VariableStringBuffer("com_errorMessage", buf, sizeof(buf));
8348 
8349  // stricmp() is silly but works, take a look at error.menu to see why.
8350  // NOTE: I'm not sure Q_stricmp is useful to anything anymore
8351  if ((*buf) && (Q_stricmp(buf, ";")))
8352  {
8353  trap_Cvar_Set("ui_connecting", "0");
8354  if (!Q_stricmpn(buf, "Invalid password", 16))
8355  {
8356  trap_Cvar_Set("com_errorMessage", trap_TranslateString(buf));
8357  Menus_ActivateByName("popupPassword", qtrue);
8358  }
8359  else if (strlen(buf) > 5 && !Q_stricmpn(buf, "ET://", 5) && strlen(buf) < 200)
8360  {
8361  if (ui_serverBrowserSettings.integer & UI_BROWSER_ALLOW_REDIRECT)
8362  {
8363  Q_strncpyz(buf, buf + 5, sizeof(buf));
8364  Com_Printf(trap_TranslateString("Server is full, redirect to: %s\n"), buf);
8365  // always prompt
8366  trap_Cvar_Set("com_errorMessage", buf);
8367  Menus_ActivateByName("popupServerRedirect", qtrue);
8368  }
8369  else
8370  {
8371  trap_Cvar_Set("com_errorMessage", "Server is full.\nRedirecting denied by cvar setting.");
8372  Menus_ActivateByName("popupError", qtrue);
8373  }
8374  }
8375  else
8376  {
8377  qboolean pb_enable = qfalse;
8378 
8379  if (strstr(buf, "must be Enabled"))
8380  {
8381  pb_enable = qtrue;
8382  }
8383 
8384  trap_Cvar_Set("com_errorMessage", trap_TranslateString(buf));
8385  // hacky, wanted to have the printout of missing files
8386  // text printing limitations force us to keep it all in a single message
8387  // NOTE: this works thanks to flip flop in UI_Cvar_VariableString
8388  if (UI_Cvar_VariableString("com_errorDiagnoseIP")[0])
8389  {
8390  missing_files = UI_Cvar_VariableString("com_missingFiles");
8391  if (missing_files[0])
8392  {
8393  trap_Cvar_Set("com_errorMessage",
8394  va("%s\n\n%s\n%s",
8395  UI_Cvar_VariableString("com_errorMessage"),
8396  trap_TranslateString(MISSING_FILES_MSG),
8397  missing_files));
8398  }
8399  }
8400  if (pb_enable)
8401  {
8402  Menus_ActivateByName("popupError_pbenable", qtrue);
8403  }
8404  else
8405  {
8406  Menus_ActivateByName("popupError", qtrue);
8407  }
8408  }
8409  }
8410 
8411  trap_S_FadeAllSound(1.0f, 1000, qfalse); // make sure sound fades up
8412  return;
8413 
8414  case UIMENU_TEAM:
8415  trap_Key_SetCatcher(KEYCATCH_UI);
8416  Menus_ActivateByName("team", qtrue);
8417  return;
8418 
8419  case UIMENU_INGAME:
8420  if (g_gameType.integer == GT_SINGLE_PLAYER)
8421  {
8422  trap_Cvar_Set("cl_paused", "1");
8423  }
8424  trap_Key_SetCatcher(KEYCATCH_UI);
8425  UI_BuildPlayerList();
8426  Menu_SetFeederSelection(NULL, FEEDER_PLAYER_LIST, 0, NULL);
8427  Menus_CloseAll();
8428  Menus_ActivateByName("ingame_main", qtrue);
8429  return;
8430 
8431  case UIMENU_WM_QUICKMESSAGE:
8432  uiInfo.uiDC.cursorx = 639;
8433  uiInfo.uiDC.cursory = 479;
8434  trap_Key_SetCatcher(KEYCATCH_UI);
8435  Menus_CloseAll();
8436  Menus_OpenByName("wm_quickmessage");
8437  return;
8438 
8439  case UIMENU_WM_QUICKMESSAGEALT:
8440  uiInfo.uiDC.cursorx = 639;
8441  uiInfo.uiDC.cursory = 479;
8442  trap_Key_SetCatcher(KEYCATCH_UI);
8443  Menus_CloseAll();
8444  Menus_OpenByName("wm_quickmessageAlt");
8445  return;
8446

8448  uiInfo.uiDC.cursorx = 639;

8547 void UI_ReadableSize(char *buf, int bufsize, int value)
8548 {
8549  if (value > 1024 * 1024 * 1024) // gigs
8550  {
8551  Com_sprintf(buf, bufsize, "%d", value / (1024 * 1024 * 1024));
8552  Com_sprintf(buf + strlen(buf), bufsize - strlen(buf), ".%02d GB",
8553  (value % (1024 * 1024 * 1024)) * 100 / (1024 * 1024 * 1024));
8554  }
8555  else if (value > 1024 * 1024) // megs
8556  {
8557  Com_sprintf(buf, bufsize, "%d", value / (1024 * 1024));
8558  Com_sprintf(buf + strlen(buf), bufsize - strlen(buf), ".%02d MB",
8559  (value % (1024 * 1024)) * 100 / (1024 * 1024));
8560  }
8561  else if (value > 1024) // kilos
8562  {
8563  Com_sprintf(buf, bufsize, "%d KB", value / 1024);
8564  }
8565  else // bytes
8566  {
8567  Com_sprintf(buf, bufsize, "%d bytes", value);
8568  }
8569 }
8570 
8577 void UI_PrintTime(char *buf, int bufsize, int time)
8578 {
8579  //time /= 1000; // change to seconds
8580 
8581  if (time > 3600) // in the hours range
8582  {
8583  Com_sprintf(buf, bufsize, "%d hr %d min", time / 3600, (time % 3600) / 60);
8584  }
8585  else if (time > 60) // mins
8586  {
8587  Com_sprintf(buf, bufsize, "%d min %d sec", time / 60, time % 60);
8588  }
8589  else // secs
8590  {
8591  Com_sprintf(buf, bufsize, "%d sec", time);
8592  }
8593 }

8868 static const unsigned int cvarTableSize = sizeof(cvarTable) / sizeof(cvarTable[0]);
8869 
8873 void UI_RegisterCvars(void)
8874 {
8875  unsigned int i;
8876  cvarTable_t *cv;
8877 
8878  Com_Printf("%u UI cvars in use\n", cvarTableSize);
8879 
8880  for (i = 0, cv = cvarTable ; i < cvarTableSize ; i++, cv++)
8881  {
8882  trap_Cvar_Register(cv->vmCvar, cv->cvarName, cv->defaultString, cv->cvarFlags);
8883  if (cv->vmCvar != NULL)
8884  {
8885  cv->modificationCount = cv->vmCvar->modificationCount;
8886  }
8887  }
8888 
8889  // Always force this to 0 on init
8890  trap_Cvar_Set("ui_blackout", "0");
8891  BG_setCrosshair(ui_cg_crosshairColor.string, uiInfo.xhairColor, ui_cg_crosshairAlpha.value, "cg_crosshairColor");
8892  BG_setCrosshair(ui_cg_crosshairColorAlt.string, uiInfo.xhairColorAlt, ui_cg_crosshairAlphaAlt.value, "cg_crosshairColorAlt");
8893 }
8894 
8898 void UI_UpdateCvars(void)
8899 {
8900  size_t i;
8901  cvarTable_t *cv;
8902 
8903  for (i = 0, cv = cvarTable ; i < cvarTableSize ; i++, cv++)
8904  {
8905  if (cv->vmCvar)
8906  {
8907  trap_Cvar_Update(cv->vmCvar);
8908  if (cv->modificationCount != cv->vmCvar->modificationCount)
8909  {
8910  cv->modificationCount = cv->vmCvar->modificationCount;
8911 
8912  if (cv->vmCvar == &ui_cg_crosshairColor || cv->vmCvar == &ui_cg_crosshairAlpha)
8913  {
8914  BG_setCrosshair(ui_cg_crosshairColor.string, uiInfo.xhairColor, ui_cg_crosshairAlpha.value, "cg_crosshairColor");
8915  }
8916 
8917  if (cv->vmCvar == &ui_cg_crosshairColorAlt || cv->vmCvar == &ui_cg_crosshairAlphaAlt)
8918  {
8919  BG_setCrosshair(ui_cg_crosshairColorAlt.string, uiInfo.xhairColorAlt, ui_cg_crosshairAlphaAlt.value, "cg_crosshairColorAlt");
8920  }
8921  }
8922  }
8923  }
8924 }

8929 static void UI_StopServerRefresh(void)
8930 {
8931  int count;
8932 
8933  if (!uiInfo.serverStatus.refreshActive)
8934  {
8935  // not currently refreshing
8936  return;
8937  }
8938  uiInfo.serverStatus.refreshActive = qfalse;
8939  Com_Printf(trap_TranslateString("%d servers listed in browser with %d players.\n"),
8940  uiInfo.serverStatus.numDisplayServers,
8941  uiInfo.serverStatus.numPlayersOnServers);
8942  count = trap_LAN_GetServerCount(ui_netSource.integer);
8943  if (count - uiInfo.serverStatus.numDisplayServers > 0)
8944  {
8945  Com_Printf(trap_TranslateString("%d servers not listed (filtered out by game browser settings)\n"),
8946  count - uiInfo.serverStatus.numDisplayServers);
8947  }
8948 }
8949 
8953 static void UI_DoServerRefresh(void)
8954 {
8955  qboolean wait = qfalse;
8956 
8957  if (!uiInfo.serverStatus.refreshActive)
8958  {
8959  return;
8960  }
8961 
8962  if (ui_netSource.integer != AS_FAVORITES)
8963  {
8964  if (ui_netSource.integer == AS_LOCAL)
8965  {
8966  if (!trap_LAN_GetServerCount(ui_netSource.integer))
8967  {
8968  wait = qtrue;
8969  }
8970  }
8971  else
8972  {
8973  if (trap_LAN_GetServerCount(ui_netSource.integer) < 0)
8974  {
8975  wait = qtrue;
8976  }
8977  }
8978  }
8979 
8980  if (uiInfo.uiDC.realTime < uiInfo.serverStatus.refreshtime)
8981  {
8982  if (wait)
8983  {
8984  return;
8985  }
8986  }
8987 
8988  // if still trying to retrieve pings
8989  if (trap_LAN_UpdateVisiblePings(ui_netSource.integer))
8990  {
8991  uiInfo.serverStatus.refreshtime = uiInfo.uiDC.realTime + 1000;
8992  }
8993  else if (!wait)
8994  {
8995  // get the last servers in the list
8996  UI_BuildServerDisplayList(2);
8997  // stop the refresh
8998  UI_StopServerRefresh();
8999  }
9000 
9001  UI_BuildServerDisplayList(0);
9002 }
9003 
9008 static void UI_StartServerRefresh(qboolean full)
9009 {
9010  char buff[64];
9011  qtime_t q;
9012 
9013  trap_RealTime(&q);
9014  Com_sprintf(buff, sizeof(buff), "%s-%i, %i at %s:%s", MonthAbbrev[q.tm_mon], q.tm_mday, 1900 + q.tm_year, q.tm_hour < 10 ? va("0%i", q.tm_hour) : va("%i", q.tm_hour),
9015  q.tm_min < 10 ? va("0%i", q.tm_min) : va("%i", q.tm_min));
9016  trap_Cvar_Set(va("ui_lastServerRefresh_%i", ui_netSource.integer), buff);
9017 
9018  if (!full)
9019  {
9020  UI_UpdatePendingPings();
9021  return;
9022  }
9023 
9024  uiInfo.serverStatus.refreshActive = qtrue;
9025  uiInfo.serverStatus.nextDisplayRefresh = uiInfo.uiDC.realTime + 1000;
9026  // clear number of displayed servers
9027  uiInfo.serverStatus.numDisplayServers = 0;
9028  uiInfo.serverStatus.numPlayersOnServers = 0;
9029  // mark all servers as visible so we store ping updates for them
9030  trap_LAN_MarkServerVisible(ui_netSource.integer, -1, qtrue);
9031  // reset all the pings
9032  trap_LAN_ResetPings(ui_netSource.integer);
9033 
9034  if (ui_netSource.integer == AS_LOCAL)
9035  {
9036  trap_Cmd_ExecuteText(EXEC_APPEND, "localservers\n");
9037  uiInfo.serverStatus.refreshtime = uiInfo.uiDC.realTime + 1000;
9038  return;
9039  }
9040 
9041  uiInfo.serverStatus.refreshtime = uiInfo.uiDC.realTime + 5000;
9042  if (ui_netSource.integer == AS_GLOBAL)
9043  {
9044  int i;
9045  for (i = 0; i < MAX_MASTER_SERVERS; i++)
9046  {
9047  if (UI_Cvar_VariableString(va("sv_master%i", i + 1))[0] != '\0')
9048  {
9049  trap_Cmd_ExecuteText(EXEC_APPEND, va("globalservers %d %d empty full\n", i, (int)(trap_Cvar_VariableValue("protocol"))));
9050  }
9051  }
9052  }
9053 }
9054 
9058 void UI_Campaign_f(void)
9059 {
9060  char str[MAX_TOKEN_CHARS];
9061  int i;
9062  campaignInfo_t *campaign = NULL;
9063 
9064  UI_LoadArenas();
9065  UI_MapCountByGameType(qfalse);
9066  UI_LoadCampaigns();
9067 
9068  // find the campaign
9069  trap_Argv(1, str, sizeof(str));
9070 
9071  for (i = 0; i < uiInfo.campaignCount; i++)
9072  {
9073  campaign = &uiInfo.campaignList[i];
9074 
9075  if (!Q_stricmp(campaign->campaignShortName, str))
9076  {
9077  break;
9078  }
9079  }
9080 
9081  if (i == uiInfo.campaignCount || !campaign || !(campaign->typeBits & (1 << GT_WOLF)))
9082  {
9083  Com_Printf(trap_TranslateString("Can't find campaign '%s'\n"), str);
9084  return;
9085  }
9086 
9087  if (!campaign->mapInfos[0])
9088  {
9089  Com_Printf(trap_TranslateString("Corrupted campaign '%s'\n"), str);
9090  return;
9091  }
9092 
9093  trap_Cvar_Set("g_currentCampaign", campaign->campaignShortName);
9094  trap_Cvar_Set("g_currentCampaignMap", "0");
9095 
9096  // we got a campaign, start it
9097  trap_Cvar_Set("g_gametype", va("%i", GT_WOLF_CAMPAIGN));
9098 
9099  trap_Cmd_ExecuteText(EXEC_APPEND, va("map %s\n", campaign->mapInfos[0]->mapLoadName));
9100 }
9101 
9105 void UI_ListCampaigns_f(void)
9106 {
9107  int i, mpCampaigns = 0;
9108 
9109  UI_LoadArenas();
9110  UI_MapCountByGameType(qfalse);
9111  UI_LoadCampaigns();
9112 
9113  for (i = 0; i < uiInfo.campaignCount; i++)
9114  {
9115  if (uiInfo.campaignList[i].typeBits & (1 << GT_WOLF))
9116  {
9117  mpCampaigns++;
9118  }
9119  }
9120 
9121  if (mpCampaigns)
9122  {
9123  Com_Printf(trap_TranslateString("%i campaigns found:\n"), mpCampaigns);
9124  }
9125  else
9126  {
9127  Com_Printf("%s", trap_TranslateString("No campaigns found.\n"));
9128  return;
9129  }
9130 
9131  for (i = 0; i < uiInfo.campaignCount; i++)
9132  {
9133  if (uiInfo.campaignList[i].typeBits & (1 << GT_WOLF))
9134  {
9135  Com_Printf(" %s\n", uiInfo.campaignList[i].campaignShortName);
9136  }
9137  }
9138 }

9147 void UI_ListFavourites_f(void)
9148 {
9149  int c;
9150 
9151  // update current status
9152  // trap_LAN_UpdateVisiblePings(AS_FAVORITES);
9153 
9154  c = trap_LAN_GetServerCount(AS_FAVORITES);
9155 
9156  if (c >= 0)
9157  {
9158  int i;
9159  char info[MAX_STRING_CHARS];
9160  char *hostinfo;
9161  char *gameinfo;
9162 
9163  for (i = 0; i < c; i++)
9164  {
9165  trap_LAN_GetServerInfo(AS_FAVORITES, i, info, MAX_STRING_CHARS);
9166 
9167  hostinfo = va("%s^7 %s", Info_ValueForKey(info, "hostname"), Info_ValueForKey(info, "game"));
9168  gameinfo = va("%s %i players", Info_ValueForKey(info, "mapname"), atoi(Info_ValueForKey(info, "clients")));
9169 
9170  Com_Printf("^7#%i: %s - %s\n", i, hostinfo, gameinfo);
9171  }
9172  }
9173  else
9174  {
9175  Com_Printf("%s\n", trap_TranslateString("No favourite servers found."));
9176  }
9177 }
